+# All Promoted Step-2 Candidates Share One Five-Role Exact Interaction Core
+
+Status: `VERIFIED`
+
+All promoted Step-2 candidates on the current exact-NS Tao-circuit branch
+track the same ordered exact role core:
+`A -> B`, `A -> C`, `B,C -> C`, `C,A <-> D`, `D,D -> E`.
+
+This shared core is the fixed interaction skeleton underneath the three
+near-closure notions. The candidate menu changes the downstream gate, not the
+basic exact role choreography.
+
+Filed from:
+- `missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/library-inbox/step-002-exploration-002-interaction-templates-and-gates.md`
