+Status: `VERIFIED`
+
+Beyond the shared five-role core, every promoted Step-2 candidate must account
+for the same forced exact-NS extras: mirror / conjugate companions,
+same-scale companion triads, long-leg feedback, and cross-scale next-shell
+feedback.
+
+These are not candidate-specific embellishments. They are the exact packet
+completions that accompany the core and help determine spectator leakage on
+the same finite window.
+
